I have the writer source now. The critical detail is that `_sellACOTokens()` never validates the ACO token and doesn’t need real option inventory for the drain to occur, so I’m replacing the separate `MaliciousAcoToken` deployment with the verifier contract itself acting as the fake ACO/collateral token.
