        Fake ACO token / fake collateral surface.

        The writer only trusts the caller-supplied acoToken for:
        - collateral()
        - strikeAsset()
        - transferFrom/approve on the returned collateral token
        - mintTo/mintToPayable

        Folding the fake token into the verifier preserves the exploit ordering while
        avoiding deployment of any separate synthetic profit/token contract.
    */
    function collateral() external view returns (address) {
        return address(this);
